      "comment": "I LOVERAIN (6) has been in good form, winning two of four runs for the new yard. Was having his first try this course and distance last time and after settling off the pace ran away with a big win. Slightly tougher but drops in weight and looks tough to stop again. FLY (1) won his first two from a spell then was runner-up behind Bruno Bruno latest in a similar race. Has the rails and will take catching. RHESUS (4) also placed behind Bruno Bruno last time in a different race and is close to a win. Wound up strongly and will be doing the same again. HELL FIRE MISS (7) is overdue and has been running on hard. Among the chances again. FUNNYIFITWON (5) is better than recent runs and is not to be underestimated.",
